Class EVMBasedQueryResultMultimap<Match extends IPatternMatch,KeyType,ValueType>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.collect.Multimap<KeyType,ValueType>

    public abstract class EVMBasedQueryResultMultimap<Match extends IPatternMatch,KeyType,ValueType>
extends QueryResultMultimap<KeyType,ValueType>
    This QueryResultMultimap implementation uses the EVM to provide a query-based multimap. The contents of the multimap will be updated when the activations are fired in the EVM.
